{"tid":2320606,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列39: 香港航空即日解僱250名機組人員","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T10:33:37.000Z","uid":292292,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"85ad6b83dca1444188cab6053f7408e380b8f5ab","tid":2320606,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:56:07.000Z","msg":"「新冠肺炎」疫情下，旅遊業近乎停頓，繼國泰航空上月宣布大幅裁減5,300名本地員工後，香港航空今日﹙11日﹚亦宣布裁員。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》收到公司管理層今早向員工發出的內部電郵，指受疫情影響，今早已解僱250名機組人員。公司稱，疫情對航空業帶來持續衝擊，為應對旅遊限制和市場需求減少，不得不在過去一年對業務進行重大調整，這些持續調整不但大大影響公司收入，也令在可預見的將來削減公司對機組人員及員工的需求，因而作出艱難的裁員決定。<br />\n<br />\n據被解僱員工透露，公司將發放12月份的薪金、一個月的代通知金；而應計但未用的年假，將在上次受僱日期的7天內結清。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》已向香港航空查詢，暫時未有回應。"},{"pid":"1cb5e238567cc28e40405f9fac1894c338cd2063","tid":2320606,"uid":167597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"又話國安法會搵大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700659fa1dc3e8cd6439e6d19e2fa8d054cc475b","tid":2320606,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1cb5e238567cc28e40405f9fac1894c338cd2063","tid":2320606,"uid":167597,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"又話國安法會搵大錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"無曬反對派 點解會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e021616732ca60c21d0ae995b84f3cb0b01e3f9","tid":2320606,"uid":180401,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T03:59:01.000Z","msg":"That good"},{"pid":"d20cf78d5797f65d07cd63adb94aaaea1454062f","tid":2320606,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T04:06:57.000Z","msg":"佔中累事😪"},{"pid":"dd79c7ed68adecc6fa6c2ebfeee64882e7703828","tid":2320606,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"700659fa1dc3e8cd6439e